  "title": "Logistic (pharma MNC) #HMS",
  "description": "<p>up to 2400<br />6 months <br />west<br /></p><p>Job scope:</p><p>Transfer of materials into cleanroom areas.</p><p>Wiping down of trolleys, equipment, furniture, and materials using chlorine 1000ppm and 70% IsoPropyl Alcohol (IPA) in cleanroom environment.</p><p>Able to plan and coordinate which materials belongs to which production batch.</p><p>Perform supporting activities such as filter integrity testing, manual cleaning, autoclave sanitization load</p><p>Perform weighing and dispensing of raw material for production batches</p><p>Perform adhoc activities as assigned<br /></p><p><br />Interested candidates, do submit your resume to: jocelynchan@recruitexpress.com.sg OR telegram @jocelynchan</p><p></p><p>Jocelyn Chan| Consultant | Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifescience)</p><p>Company EA Licence number : 99C4599</p><p>Personnel EA License: R1331820</p>",
